=== EVENT_ION_STORM ===
# id: 27
# title: Ion Storm
# chinese_title: 离子风暴
# category: AnomalyEncounter
# mode: starmap

A massive ion storm rolls across your path, crackling with energy that could fry your systems — or charge your batteries.

* [Push through at full speed]
  ~ shield_damage(10)
  冲 (chōng) — charge
* [Take shelter behind a moon and wait it out]
  ~ lose_fuel(3)
  等待 (děngdài) — wait
* [Ride the storm's edge to harvest energy] {requires: crew_role == 2}
  ~ gain_fuel(4)
  能量 (néngliàng) — energy
